data.description: *Multiple Offers Received* Final and Best due by noon 11/28* Step into this modern and meticulously updated 3/4 bedroom Cape Cod in the wonderful Lehighton Borough, PA.  Upon entering the property, you are greeted by a brand new completely updated kitchen with stainless steel appliances and large center island. The charm of original hardwood floors graces the entire first floor, seamlessly blending classic elegance with modern design. Indulge in convenience with a main floor bedroom, providing flexibility and ease of access for those looking for an alternative to a ranch home. The recently renovated full bathroom showcases stylish tile floors and a pristine shower, while the second floor boasts an additional half bathroom for added convenience to the two additional bedrooms. Parking is a breeze with a detached garage and a new blacktop driveway. Enjoy the privacy of a corner lot and the convenience of a large fenced-in yard, perfect for entertaining or quiet relaxation. This home not only offers style but is also strategically located close to downtown, just minutes away from the new Lehigh Valley Hospital. Shopping is at your fingertips, and with only a 10-minute drive to the turnpike, your commute has never been more convenient. Don't miss out on the chance to call this house your home. Schedule a viewing today and experience the perfect blend of modern luxury, classic charm, and thoughtful convenience!
